    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of various aqueous treaments to remove dirt or other unwanted surface materials. In commercial garment cleaning, the term is used interchangeably with "green cleansing" to describe gentle, environmentally friendly aqueous cleansing. In conservation context: washing of textiles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
